buat kerja seperti awak.

252
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,359
Awak tak nak saya

253
00:13:48,719 --> 00:13:50,719
buat pilihan seperti awak.

254
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:54,159
Sebab awak tahu

255
00:13:54,919 --> 00:13:56,840
ini amat memenatkan.

256
00:13:58,599 --> 00:14:00,799
Namun, saya lebih jelas daripada awak

257
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:04,159
kerana saya asyik pandang awak.

258
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,840
Selama ini,

259
00:14:08,119 --> 00:14:09,440
awak buat banyak perkara

260
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:10,960
demi rakyat,

261
00:14:11,479 --> 00:14:12,640
baginda

262
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:15,280
dan tuanku.

263
00:14:18,719 --> 00:14:20,080
Namun, tiada orang

264
00:14:20,599 --> 00:14:22,960
benar-benar buat sesuatu demi awak.

265
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,520
Kali ini,

266
00:14:34,359 --> 00:14:36,640
tukarlah saya buat sesuatu demi awak.

267
00:14:39,799 --> 00:14:42,039
Biar saya melindungi awak.

268
00:14:47,919 --> 00:14:49,960
Saya pasti akan selamatkan awak.

269
00:14:52,039 --> 00:14:53,520
Jangan cakap

270
00:14:54,039 --> 00:14:55,119
saya masih dapat rasa bahagia

271
00:14:56,119 --> 00:14:58,000
selepas awak dah meninggal.

272
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,359
Awaklah satu-satunya

273
00:15:05,159 --> 00:15:06,320
kebahagiaan saya.

274
00:16:14,930 --> 00:16:17,930
(Kota Tianqi)

275
00:16:21,010 --> 00:16:33,450
(Jiuyuan)

276
00:16:45,239 --> 00:16:45,919
Macam mana?

277
00:16:46,239 --> 00:16:46,919
Yang mulia.

278
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,359
Kematian penolong utusan Nihualuo

279
00:16:48,559 --> 00:16:50,359
mencetuskan masalah besar di ibu kota.

280
00:16:50,679 --> 00:16:51,520
Pasukan utusan nihualuo

281
00:16:51,760 --> 00:16:53,039
dah hantar orang balik ke puak

282
00:16:53,239 --> 00:16:55,760
dan kata mereka takkan biar
perkara ini diakhiri dengan baik.

283
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:57,440
Mereka akan lapor kepada raja mereka

284
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:58,960
dan mulakan peperangan.

285
00:16:59,559 --> 00:17:01,000
Sekarang,

286
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:03,119
baginda dah sakit kepala.

287
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:04,760
Baik.

288
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:08,000
Adakah Fang Haishi
buat apa-apa tindakan?

289
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,599
Dia tinggal di Istana Fengwu

290
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:10,839
dan tak keluar dari sana.

291
00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:13,439
Istana Fengwu juga
ditambah bilangan pengawal.

292
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:15,560
Nampaknya dia tercedera

293
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:17,280
dan tak dapat pergi ke Negeri Yue.

294
00:17:17,719 --> 00:17:20,599
Nihualuo dah nak mulakan peperangan.

295
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:21,839
Jika Fang Haishi tak dapat

296
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,680
jemput Dewa Ekor Naga dengan segera...

297
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:24,880
Jika dia tak dapat
jemput Dewa Ekor Naga,

298
00:17:25,119 --> 00:17:26,359
bukan sahaja Nihualuo,

299
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:28,079
duta puak lain

300
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:29,839
juga takkan lepaskan Da Zheng.

301
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:33,199
Apakah berita dari Genting Huangquan?

302
00:17:33,479 --> 00:17:35,599
Tang Qianzi dah terima titah maharaja

303
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:37,239
yang mengarahkan Fu Yi
dan Zhang Chengqian

304
00:17:37,479 --> 00:17:38,640
bawa 50 ribu orang tentera

305
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,319
bergegas balik ke Kota Tianqi.

306
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:41,719
Baik.

307
00:17:43,199 --> 00:17:44,280
Dengan ada Fu Yi,

308
00:17:45,119 --> 00:17:46,920
maka, tentera ini adalah tentera saya.

309
00:17:56,839 --> 00:17:58,800
Saya akan ditegur Kak Bi Zi lagi.

310
00:18:14,599 --> 00:18:15,560
Apa?

311
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:17,839
Ubat mengukuhkan janin Ti Lan beracun?

312
00:18:18,119 --> 00:18:19,199
Ya, tuanku.

313
00:18:19,479 --> 00:18:20,319
Dayang-dayang di Istana Yu'an

314
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:22,239
tertuang ubat itu.

315
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,040
Siapa tahu

316
00:18:23,199 --> 00:18:25,800
bunga dan rumput
yang terkena ubat dah layu.

317
00:18:27,959 --> 00:18:28,800
Bahagian mana

318
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:29,599
bermasalah?

319
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:31,800
Hamba dah kerahkan orang
untuk menyiasat dengan teliti.

320
00:18:32,119 --> 00:18:34,680
Namun, tak kira sisa ubat,

321
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,959
tabib diraja, dayang-dayang

322
00:18:36,119 --> 00:18:37,560
atau proses penghantaran ubat,

323
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:39,479
semuanya tiada masalah.

324
00:18:39,719 --> 00:18:40,719
Tak guna!

325
00:18:48,119 --> 00:18:50,040
Orang itu bubuh racun dalam ubat itu,

326
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,239
maka, dia tahu

327
00:18:51,319 --> 00:18:52,359
Ti Lan hamil.

328
00:18:52,599 --> 00:18:54,000
Dia tak boleh tinggal
di Istana Yu'an lagi.

329
00:18:54,760 --> 00:18:55,479
Mu Deqing.

330
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:56,400
Ya.

331
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:57,560
Bawa Ti Lan

332
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:59,040
untuk tinggal di Istana Jincheng
dengan diam-diam.

333
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:00,680
Bawa seorang dayang-dayang sahaja,
iaitu Bi Zi.

334
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,400
Orang lain di Istana Yu'an

335
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,680
dikurung di sana.

336
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:04,319
Siasat dengan teliti

337
00:19:04,479 --> 00:19:06,119
dan mesti cari orang yang bubuh racun.

338
00:19:06,479 --> 00:19:07,839
Junjung titah tuanku.

339
00:19:13,359 --> 00:19:14,800
Bagaimana dengan Jianming?

340
00:19:15,760 --> 00:19:17,040
Tuanku.

341
00:19:17,839 --> 00:19:18,319
Baru-baru ini,

342
00:19:18,479 --> 00:19:20,199
Tuan Qing Hai makan ubat patik

343
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:21,520
dan asyik tidur.

344
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:24,079
Mungkin emosi dia tenang,

345
00:19:24,239 --> 00:19:24,959
badan dia juga

346
00:19:25,119 --> 00:19:26,199
dapat berehat dengan secukupnya.

347
00:19:26,719 --> 00:19:28,520
Nadi dia lebih baik

348
00:19:28,719 --> 00:19:29,880
daripada dulu.

349
00:19:30,239 --> 00:19:30,880
Bagus.

350
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:34,280
Serbuk Mutiara Naga itu...

351
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:35,719
Tinggal sedikit sahaja.

352
00:19:39,479 --> 00:19:40,839
Baik, keluarlah.

353
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:42,959
Beta nak bercakap dengan Jianming.

354
00:19:44,199 --> 00:19:45,160
Junjung titah tuanku.

355
00:20:01,959 --> 00:20:03,119
Jianming.

356
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,040
Sejak awak tidur,

357
00:20:07,959 --> 00:20:09,560
banyak perkara dah berlaku.

358
00:20:10,439 --> 00:20:11,680
Tentera laut Nihualuo

359
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,520
dah tiba di kawasan barat daya.

360
00:20:14,079 --> 00:20:15,880
Peperangan bakal dicetuskan.

361
00:20:16,560 --> 00:20:18,199
Duta dari semua puak

362
00:20:18,959 --> 00:20:20,800
dah tiba di Kota Tianqi.

363
00:20:21,359 --> 00:20:23,520
Keadaan kita bahaya.

364
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:26,880
Di istana...

365
00:20:29,959 --> 00:20:31,920
Di istana, ada orang
nak menganiayai Ti Lan

366
00:20:32,199 --> 00:20:33,560
dan anak kami.

367
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:44,599
Asalnya beta ingat

368
00:20:45,839 --> 00:20:46,560
masa itu, kita

369
00:20:46,719 --> 00:20:48,439
dah meredakan Pemberontakan Raja Yi,

370
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,319
bunuh musuh di Tanah Hongyao,

371
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:52,040
hapuskan Panglima Enam Sayap

372
00:20:52,439 --> 00:20:53,680
dan buat pelbagai rancangan,

373
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:56,680
maka, kita dah selesaikan
semua masalah itu

374
00:20:57,719 --> 00:20:59,439
dan negara kita dah aman damai.

375
00:21:00,719 --> 00:21:02,239
Namun, tak sangka,

376
00:21:03,439 --> 00:21:04,400
sampai sekarang,

377
00:21:06,119 --> 00:21:08,599
negara kita masih terancam.

378
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,280
Memang

379
00:21:18,719 --> 00:21:20,479
selagi kita berada di sini,

380
00:21:21,520 --> 00:21:25,400
maka, ada cabaran yang tak terhingga.

381
00:21:26,199 --> 00:21:27,560
Namun, jangan risau.

382
00:21:29,079 --> 00:21:30,160
Beta

383
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,160
dah dapat mengawal keadaan

384
00:21:34,359 --> 00:21:36,479
dan takkan ada masalah
untuk sementara waktu ini.

385
00:21:38,079 --> 00:21:39,280
Selepas awak dah sedar diri,

386
00:21:40,479 --> 00:21:42,839
awak tahu Fang Haishi
pergi jemput Lang Huan,

387
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:47,359
rasanya awak akan
berpaling muka dengan beta lagi.

388
00:22:03,040 --> 00:22:04,839
Pindah pada awal pagi esok?

389
00:22:05,199 --> 00:22:06,599
Begitu tergesa-gesa nak pindah?

390
00:22:09,040 --> 00:22:10,439
Ia menyusahkan awak.

391
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,599
Tak.

392
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:14,400
Adinda berterima kasih

393
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:16,439
atas niat kakanda.

394
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:19,839
Ketika beta masih kecil,

395
00:22:20,599 --> 00:22:22,079
beta pernah baca sebuah sajak.

396
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:25,040
Sajak itu berbunyi seperti berikut,

397
00:22:26,599 --> 00:22:28,520
benda bagus di dunia tak kekal lama,

398
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:32,199
awan dan kaca mudah pecah.

399
00:22:34,319 --> 00:22:35,199
Ti Lan.

400
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:37,640
Dari kecil hingga besar,

401
00:22:38,839 --> 00:22:41,040
perkara dan orang baik

402
00:22:42,239 --> 00:22:43,160
di sisi beta,

403
00:22:46,319 --> 00:22:49,079
akan tinggalkan beta.

404
00:22:54,959 --> 00:22:56,160
Maka, Ti Lan

405
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,560
jadi awan dan kaca

406
00:22:59,079 --> 00:23:00,880
yang tak pecah.

407
00:23:03,560 --> 00:23:04,359
Awak berjanji dengan beta ya.

408
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,319
Perkara yang dah dijanjikan

409
00:23:06,599 --> 00:23:07,640
tak boleh dimungkiri.

410
00:23:08,760 --> 00:23:10,160
Takkan menyesal.

411
00:25:10,870 --> 00:25:17,330
♪Menanggung penderitaan akibat kerinduan
dan mendongak bersungut kepada bulan♪

412
00:25:18,290 --> 00:25:24,240
♪Tak dapat sentuh kamu,
hanya dapat berhubung dengan angin♪

413
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:32,620
♪Perasaan ini berlarutan
hingga ke penghujung hayat♪

414
00:25:33,710 --> 00:25:39,850
♪Hidup ini tak sia-sia
dengan adanya awak♪

415
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:44,140
♪Saya ingin pegang lampu♪

416
00:25:44,900 --> 00:25:48,160
♪Dan menemani awak berjalan pulang♪

417
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:55,080
♪Tidak kira puisi cinta atau
mata yang bergenang air mata♪

418
00:25:59,290 --> 00:26:01,940
♪Harap saya kejarnya seumur hidup♪

419
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:07,000
♪Suci dan dilindungi oleh cinta♪

420
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:11,470
♪Harap saya ikut jejak awak,
hujan renyai-renyai pagi dan malam♪

421
00:26:11,730 --> 00:26:14,350
♪Menyembuhkan parut♪

422
00:26:14,930 --> 00:26:19,150
♪Harap saya yang muda
mengenang orang yang sudah tiada♪

423
00:26:19,340 --> 00:26:22,220
♪Biarpun kecewa♪

424
00:26:22,670 --> 00:26:28,370
♪Terima kasih atas sanjungan awak,
terakhir bagaikan permulaan♪

425
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:33,020
♪Sekali dalam seumur hidup♪

426
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:44,080
♪Hati berdebar♪

427
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:03,760
♪Jatuh bangun beberapa tahun itu♪

428
00:27:03,761 --> 00:27:07,650
♪Perpisahan bagaikan
jalan yang mesti dilalui♪

429
00:27:08,500 --> 00:27:14,330
♪Surat-menyurat, tercatat hanya isi hati
dan tiada penderitaan♪

430
00:27:16,050 --> 00:27:19,510
♪Saya ingin pegang lampu♪

431
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:23,350
♪Dan menemani awak berjalan pulang♪

432
00:27:23,730 --> 00:27:30,070
♪Tidak kira puisi cinta atau
mata yang bergenang air mata♪

433
00:27:30,710 --> 00:27:35,380
♪Harap saya kejarnya seumur hidup♪

434
00:27:35,570 --> 00:27:38,130
♪Suci dan dilindungi oleh cinta♪

435
00:27:38,680 --> 00:27:41,560
♪Harap saya ikut jejak awak,
hujan renyai-renyai pagi dan malam♪

436
00:27:41,560 --> 00:27:43,599
(Betulkah awak nak melindungi dia
sampai tahap ini?)

437
00:27:43,959 --> 00:27:45,479
(Untuk biar dia tak rasa serba salah,)

438
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:47,119
awak tak pedulikan Da Zheng,

439
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,359
beta

440
00:27:48,560 --> 00:27:49,239
dan nyawa sendiri?

441
00:27:49,439 --> 00:27:50,160
Patik tak nak

442
00:27:50,359 --> 00:27:52,359
dia menjadi Fang Jianming kedua.

443
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:54,719
Sebab hanya patik faham

444
00:27:55,280 --> 00:27:57,119
kesengsaraan Fang Jianming.

445
00:27:57,439 --> 00:27:59,479
Patik tak menyesal
dengan hidup seperti ini.

446
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:02,040
Patik cuma harap orang kesayangan patik

447
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:04,119
dapat hidup dengan biasa dan bahagia.

448
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,560
Tuanku jangan risau.

449
00:28:06,199 --> 00:28:08,199
Patik pasti akan cuba sedaya upaya

450
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:10,520
untuk bawa Lang Huan
balik ke Kota Tianqi.

451
00:28:10,719 --> 00:28:12,359
Diminta tuanku berkenan dengan patik

452
00:28:13,239 --> 00:28:14,880
untuk melindungi Lang Huan dengan baik.

453
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:17,040
Jangan biar dia tercedera.

454
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:22,970
♪Harap tangan dikotori tanah,
tak reti susah♪

455
00:28:23,230 --> 00:28:25,920
♪Tetap mengira setiap kuntum bunga♪

456
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:26,760
Haishi,

457
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:29,710
jangan sedih.

458
00:28:29,719 --> 00:28:32,280
♪Harap saya alami banyak cabaran♪

459
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:33,000
Saya tahu

460
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:35,479
awak serba salah.

461
00:28:36,599 --> 00:28:37,599
Saya juga tahu awak buat begini

462
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:40,479
bukannya demi diri awak.

463
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:45,280
Saya sudi ikut awak balik ke Tianqi.

464
00:28:45,470 --> 00:28:47,880
♪Terima kasih atas sanjungan awak,
terakhir bagaikan permulaan♪

465
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,040
Lang Huan,

466
00:28:50,119 --> 00:28:51,400
saya tak dapat

467
00:28:52,079 --> 00:28:53,640
balas jasa awak.

468
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,760
Baginda dah arahkan orang

469
00:28:58,199 --> 00:28:59,000
pergi cari kayu hitam

470
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:00,560
yang dah direndam banyak tahun
di bawah laut.

471
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,239
Ia direndam minyak tung

472
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:04,199
dan diisikan air laut.

473
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:06,239
Ini cara He Luo

474
00:29:06,560 --> 00:29:07,560
yang menjamin air laut

475
00:29:07,760 --> 00:29:09,479
takkan berubah dalam masa tiga tahun.

476
00:29:10,280 --> 00:29:11,079
Saya tahu

477
00:29:11,839 --> 00:29:13,160
perjalanan ini bahaya.

478
00:29:14,560 --> 00:29:15,719
Namun, saya bersumpah,

479
00:29:16,040 --> 00:29:17,839
saya akan melindungi awak
dengan nyawa sendiri.

480
00:29:18,599 --> 00:29:19,800
Jangan risau.

481
00:29:20,599 --> 00:29:21,560
Selepas tinggalkan sini,

482
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:24,160
mungkin saya tak rasa bebas lagi

483
00:29:24,319 --> 00:29:25,479
seperti saya di dalam laut.

484
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,400
Namun, di dunia ini,

485
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:30,479
ada banyak perkara yang susah.

486
00:29:31,239 --> 00:29:32,280
Kita tak boleh larikan diri

487
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:34,959
hanya disebabkan berdepan
dengan kesusahan.

488
00:29:36,560 --> 00:29:37,719
Kali ini, saya pergi ke Da Zheng.

489
00:29:38,439 --> 00:29:41,160
Mungkin saya boleh meredakan peperangan

490
00:29:41,439 --> 00:29:42,520
dan saya dapat bantu awak.

491
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,479
Jadi, ia adalah berbaloi.

492
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:51,479
Salam sejahtera, Maharaja Da Zheng.

493
00:29:53,800 --> 00:29:54,439
Bangun.

494
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:56,079
Junjung kasih Maharaja Da Zheng.

